#| "<trademark>Rubik's Cube </trademark> puzzle."
msgid ""
"&kubrick; was inspired by Professor Ern&odblac; Rubik's famous "
"<trademark>Rubik's Cube </trademark> puzzle."
msgstr ""
"&kubrick;u inspiratsiooniallikaks oli professor Ernö Rubiku kuulus "
"<trademark>Rubiku kuubik</trademark>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:876
